1
00:00:00,791 --> 00:00:02,041
Some time after my release

2
00:00:02,125 --> 00:00:05,875
ISIS members returned to search for my father

3
00:00:06,083 --> 00:00:08,083
Every day or two, they came back

4
00:00:08,208 --> 00:00:09,875
They knew my brother had fled to Qamishli

5
00:00:10,333 --> 00:00:12,291
But my father hadn’t left the area

6
00:00:12,833 --> 00:00:16,041
And ISIS members knew that

7
00:00:16,166 --> 00:00:18,000
So they came regularly asking about him

8
00:00:19,750 --> 00:00:21,333
And about my brother too

9
00:00:21,708 --> 00:00:25,375
They also used to summon my other brother

10
00:00:26,708 --> 00:00:29,083
To ask him about my father and my brother

11
00:00:29,250 --> 00:00:31,958
When they would come, and
which relatives we were in touch with

12
00:00:32,166 --> 00:00:33,916
They pressured us heavily

13
00:00:34,375 --> 00:00:36,750
Trying to make us leave the area

14
00:00:36,875 --> 00:00:39,041
They clearly didn’t want us there at all

15
00:00:41,375 --> 00:00:43,583
They repeated the same interrogations with my nephew too

16
00:00:44,250 --> 00:00:47,791
They also took our ID cards

17
00:00:48,541 --> 00:00:52,041
From me, my brothers, and my cousins, and never returned them

18
00:00:52,541 --> 00:00:55,916
But they did give us back our mobile phones

19
00:00:56,125 --> 00:00:57,791
They said it was forbidden to return IDs

20
00:00:57,958 --> 00:00:59,500
We followed up with them about the IDs

21
00:00:59,666 --> 00:01:01,583
Until they started threatening to imprison us if we asked again

22
00:01:01,708 --> 00:01:03,333
They told us to forget about them

23
00:01:04,416 --> 00:01:08,833
Then I realized they might use the IDs to escape someday

24
00:01:12,875 --> 00:01:18,125
So we stopped asking about them altogether

25
00:01:19,125 --> 00:01:22,333
They issued us identification cards instead

26
00:01:26,333 --> 00:01:29,083
After we had attended a sharia course

27
00:01:29,208 --> 00:01:32,416
To receive the ID card that became mandatory

28
00:01:33,125 --> 00:01:34,708
We started showing them at checkpoints

29
00:01:34,833 --> 00:01:36,208
Unable to move without them
